        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2064056276" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17971146109984765865">This has been on our family book shelf f-o-r-e-v-e-r. Sorry I took so long to actually read it. It is marvelous! The main protagonist, nine-year old Cassie Logan, is also the delightful narrator. Excellent, if not sobering way to introduce middle schoolers+ to racism in America in the 1930s.<br/><br/>I cannot help wondering what kind of equivalent book will be written about our era for the young people of tomorrow... </span>

          </span>
        </div>


