<span id="freeTextContainer11465769107711134283">It&apos;s amazing to us that this book is forty years old. It&apos;s as powerful and relevant now as it was in 1976, perhaps even more so. <i>
  <blockquote>White is something just like black is something. Everybody born on this earth is something and nobody, no matter what color, is better than anybody else.</blockquote>
